data.value:
Ichki yorliqlar ilova ichida cheklangan. Bu aslida mo'ljallangan variant emas, lekin siz qanday yorliqlarni globaletay qilish niyatida bo'lishingizni rejalashtirishingiz mumkin.
Odatiy ravishda barcha global yorliqlar yoqilgan. TheShow / O'rta oynaning asosiy derazasshorttutni qulflash tugmachasi uchun ishlatish. Siz har qanday vaqtda marshrut yoki imo-ishorani o'zgartirishingiz mumkin. Butorat uni sinab ko'ring
data.comment:
• InternalAll shortcuts are limited to within the application. This is not really an intended option but can allow to customize what shortcuts you intend to make globalsomeday.
  • Default All global shortcuts are enabled. TheShow/Hide Main Windowshortcut usesoverriderouting for theCaps Lock key. You can change that routing or gesture at any time. Butgive it a try

data.name: ShortcutRoutingTypeHint
data.value:
Global yorliq rejimlari
Passiv maykaype har qanday qo'llanuvda tinglaydi.
* Bu endi Linux-dagi yagona variant.
Faol dastur orqali ishlov berishdan oldin olding old qismini bajaradi.
Qisqadan keyin Faol dastur orqali ishlangandan keyin joylashtiring.
Monkeyp pastligi qisqartirishning qisqartirilganligini (o'zgaruvchan tugmachasini) ko'rib chiqish tugmachasini tinglaydi, bu kalitdan foydalanish tugmachasini - darajadagi kirish tugmachasini yashiradi.
Ushbu parametr yorliqni faol dasturga ziddiyatsiz qabul qilmasdan boshšar ekanligiga kafolat beradi.
Eksklyuziv bekor qilish - bu Caps Lock tugmachasi uchun mo'ljallangan bekor qilish rejimining maxsus turi. Bu faqat bitta kalit (o'zgaruvchan bo'lmagan) uni tayinlash uchun ruxsat beradi.
Oddiy foydalanish rejimida Caps Lock boshqa kalitlar bilan birgalikda bosilganda yopishtirilishi mumkin.
Shunday qilib, boshqa tugmachalar nimadan qat'i nazar, agar hotchey yorliq bosilsa, u bekor qilinadi va uni yopishib olishiga yo'l qo'ymaydi.
data.comment:
Global Shortcut Modes

  • Passive A shortcut MonkeyPaste will listen for in any application.
    *This is the only option on Linux for now.
  • Pre Shortcut will execute before it is handled by the active application.
  • Post Shortcut will execute after it is handled by the active application.
  • Override When MonkeyPaste hears the input key (non - modifier key) of an override shortcut it will hide that key press from application - level input.
    This option will guarantee the shortcut is triggered without conflicts to the active application.
  • Exclusive Override This is a special type of override mode designed for the Caps Lock key. It only allows one key (non - modifier) for its assignment.
    In normal override mode Caps Lock can become stuck on when pressed in combination with other keys.
    So no matter what other keys are down, if a Hotkey shortcut is pressed it will be overriden and prevent it from becoming stuck on.
